==定年、解析和影響==
對阿拉瓜伊尼亚陨石坑地質構造最早的研究報告於1969年由 Northfleet 等人發表，該論文指出當地的上升區域是[[白堊紀|白堊紀]]的[[正長岩|正長岩]][[侵入_(地質學)|侵入]][[顯生宙|顯生宙]]的沉積岩造成<ref>Northfleet, A. A.; Medeiros, R.A.; Muhlmann, H. 1969. Reavaliação dos dados geológicos da Bacia do Paraná. Boletim Técnico da Petrobrás, 12:291-346.</ref>。Silveira Filho 和 Ribeiro 在1971年對當地進行更詳細的地質調查，指出在中心區域周圍有[[熔岩|熔岩]]、[[角礫岩|角礫岩]]和[[凝灰岩|凝灰岩]]的存在，並提出當地是[[隱爆作用|潛火山結構]]的結論<ref>Silveira Filho, N. C.; Ribeiro, C. L. 1971. Informações geológicas preliminares sobre a estrutura vulcânica de Araguainha, Mato Grosso. DNPM/Distrito Centro-Leste (relatório interno).</ref>。1973年[[羅伯特·迪茨|羅伯特·迪茨]]和 B.M. French 的研究報告指出發現了撞擊角礫岩和[[衝擊石英|衝擊石英]]，確認它是隕石坑<ref>Dietz, R. S.; French, B. M. 1973. [http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v244/n5418/abs/244561a0.html Two probable astroblemes in Brazil.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v244/n5418/abs/244561a0.html |date=20190713121128 }} [[自然_(期刊)|Nature]], 244:561-562.</ref><ref>Dietz, R. S.; French, B. M.; Oliveira, M. A. M. 1973. Araguainha Dome (Goiás) and Serra da Cangalha (Mato Grosso): probable astroblemes? In: SBG, Congresso Brasileiro de Geologia, 27, Resumo das Comunicações, 1:102.</ref>。[[阿爾瓦羅·彭特亞多·克羅斯塔|阿爾瓦羅·彭特亞多·克羅斯塔]]在1981和1982年發表的論文中提出更多[[岩石學|岩石學]]和[[礦物學|礦物學]]上的證據進一步證明當地是隕石坑<ref>Crósta, A. P. 1982. Mapeamento geológico do Domo de Araguainha utilizando técnicas de sensoriamento remoto. Instituto Nacional de Pesquisas Espaciais (INPE), São José dos Campos. Dissertação de Mestrado 90 p.</ref><ref>Crósta, A. P., Gaspar; J. C.; Candia, M. A. F 1981. Feições de metamorfismo de impacto no Domo de Araguainha. Revista Brasileira de Geociências, 11: 139-146.</ref>。Theilen-Willige 於1981年發表的論文則是從[[地貌學|地貌學]]的角度提出它是隕石坑的證據<ref>Theilen-Willige, B. 1981. The Araguainha impact structure, Central Brazil. Revista Brasileira de Geociências, 11:91-97.</ref>。Deutsch 等人於1992年首次對阿拉瓜伊尼亚陨石坑以[[銣鍶定年法|銣鍶定年法]]定年（2.43 ± 0.19億年）<ref>Deutsch, A.; Buhl, D.; Langenhorst, F. 1992. [http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/0040195192901675 On the significance of crater ages: new ages for Dellen (Sweden) and Araguainha (Brazil).] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/0040195192901675 |date=20190713121127 }} Tectonophysics, 216:205-218.</ref>。Engelhardt 等人同樣於1992年發表了對該隕石坑中心隆起處詳細調查後的結果，並提出2.46億年的定年結果，之後再改為2.44億年<ref>Engelhardt, W. v.; Matthäi, S. K.; Walzebuck, J. 1992. [http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1945-5100.1992.tb00226.x/abstract Araguainha impact crater, Brazil. 1. The interior part of the uplift] {{Wayback|url=http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1945-5100.1992.tb00226.x/abstract |date=20190713121127 }}. Meteoritics, 27:442-457.</ref>。Fischer 和 Masero 則在1994年時對當地進行地磁調查<ref>Fischer, G.; Masero, W. 1994. [http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1365-246X.1994.tb00141.x/abstract Rotational properties of the magnetotelluric impendance tensor – the example of the Araguainha impact crater, Brazil.] {{Wayback|url=http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1365-246X.1994.tb00141.x/abstract |date=20160305223410 }} Geophysical Journal International, 119:548-560.</ref>。

阿拉瓜伊尼亚陨石坑最新的定年結果是2.547 ± 0.025億年，上方被二疊－三疊紀交界的地層覆蓋<ref>[http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0016703712001457 Geochronological constraints on the age of a Permo–Triassic impact event: U–Pb and 40Ar/39Ar results for the 40 km Araguainha structure of central Brazil] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0016703712001457 |date=20150924152952 }}. E. Tohver, C. Lana, P.A. Cawood, I.R. Fletcher, F. Jourdan, S. Sherlock, B. Rasmussen, R.I.F. Trindade, E. Yokoyama, C.R. Souza Filho, Y. Marangoni. Geochimica et Cosmochimica Acta. Volume 86, 1 June 2012, Pages 214–227.</ref>。許多當地的岩石是[[油頁岩|油頁岩]]。形成該隕石坑的能量釋放經計算並不足以直接導致全球性滅絕事件，但巨大的震動會使當地大量的石油和天然氣從受震岩石中被釋放。這次撞擊事件也許使全球暖化突然發生，加快了[[二叠纪－三叠纪灭绝事件|二叠纪－三叠纪灭绝事件]]的過程<ref>[http://www.news.uwa.edu.au/201307315921/international/biggest-extinction-history-caused-climate-changing-meteor Biggest extinction in history caused by climate-changing meteor] {{Wayback|url=http://www.news.uwa.edu.au/201307315921/international/biggest-extinction-history-caused-climate-changing-meteor |date=20130815024027 }}. [[西澳大学|University of Western Australia]] University News Wednesday, 31 July 2013.</ref>。

==造訪路線和保護==
可從[[戈亚尼亚|戈亚尼亚]]或[[库亚巴|库亚巴]]開車到達阿拉瓜伊尼亚陨石坑。該隕石坑中心隆起處被[[阿拉瓜伊尼亚|阿拉瓜伊尼亚]]和[[蓬蒂布兰卡|蓬蒂布兰卡]]之間的無鋪面公路[[MT-306|MT-306]]穿過。直到1999年以前當地居民並不了解該隕石坑的性質以及在科學上的重要性<ref name=Cro99/>。

